      *****************************************************************
      *    保険組合せマスター読込
      *****************************************************************
       910-HKNCOMBI-READ-SEC         SECTION.
      *
           MOVE    "DBFETCH"           TO  MCP-FUNC
           CALL    "ORCMCPSUB"         USING
                                       MCPAREA
